{"tid":1886790,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警察夫婦受中國領事館職員惡待後向蘋果日報求救","createTime":"2020-02-19T06:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T07:03:02.000Z","uid":45952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"011ea8cdf9e42dee023493d812328eaeebffeaf7","tid":1886790,"uid":45952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"2012歌詩達協和號觸礁事故<br />\n<br />\n一對香港警察夫婦與親友經歷驚險場面逃難，他們6人形容事發時一片混亂，船長更一度聲稱只是機件故障。6個人在甲板重遇，一齊逃生，由4樓游繩至2樓時，郵輪已經45度傾斜，有一艘救援船駛近，六人決定一博，由大約兩層樓高位置跳落救生艇，幸好沒有受傷。一行六人之後幾經辛苦抵達羅馬後向中國駐義大利大使館求助，但受領事館職員惡待，因而在1月15日星期日致電蘋果日報求救，希望香港政府正視及協助<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AD%8C%E8%A9%A9%E9%81%94%E5%8D%94%E5%92%8C%E8%99%9F%E8%A7%B8%E7%A4%81%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2599%259F%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E7%25A4%2581%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=1502d9a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AD%8C%E8%A9%A9%E9%81%94%E5%8D%94%E5%92%8C%E8%99%9F%E8%A7%B8%E7%A4%81%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85</a><br />\n<br />\n如果仲係警隊撐大陸真心希望佢全家係鑽石公主瀨多鑊"},{"pid":"e4646b19bd713babc746a33e8bb1b4d52726cfbe","tid":1886790,"uid":58209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/14/yoFTHp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2FyoFTHp.gif&h=adbc4f41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19148948519454d22ab5dc6fdb32fe9c2a368dc4","tid":1886790,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"中國越黎越文明架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab4af9bc03d86634a93d6ca78e48e20a6ce0b9e","tid":1886790,"uid":170160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:51: